message:
"A lot of people are misinformed about the closing down of Backpage and Craigslist," said Lazenko. "Our fight hasn't ended. It has caused us more challenges."

This is why at ERASE we feel it’s important to provide law enforcement continued training on identifying and investigating human trafficking crimes. Your donation can help educate officers on the changing trends in human trafficking.

attachments.media_description: Human trafficking survivors caution that trafficking continues despite Backpage shutting down
